rComments: Absolutely loved Michael as a prof and a friend.  Michael cares about his students and provided me with tons of guidance and feedback.  I am 14 years removed from his class, yet his guidance has stuck with me all these years.  I would not be the photographer/artist/father I am today without his excellence pedagogy and opinion. Thanks Michael, Jamie
